---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Woods & Silence | Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
description: "Fine art landscape photography collection exploring forests, silence and the intimate relationship between light and nature."
---

<section class="collection-hero">
  <img src="/assets/images/woods.PNG" alt="Fine art forest landscape from the Woods and Silence collection">

  <div class="collection-hero-content">
    <p class="subtitle">Collection 01</p>
    <h1>Woods & Silence</h1>
    <p>Where silence becomes visible.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="fine-art-story">

  <div class="story-text">
    <p>
      In the quiet of the woods, light becomes slower. Every branch, shadow and reflection seems to hold its breath.
    </p>
  </div>

{% for photo in woods %}

<figure class="story-image {{ photo.class }} reveal">
    <img 
  src="{{ photo.src }}" 
  alt="{{ photo.alt }}"
     loading="lazy"
   decoding="async"
  class="lightbox-image"
  data-full="{{ photo.src }}"
  data-title=""
>
</figure>

{% endfor %}

</section>